The alpha PR/periodic job config will need to opt into this test. See config in https://github.com/kubernetes/test-infra/ for:
* pull-kubernetes-e2e-gce-alpha-features
* ci-kubernetes-e2e-gci-gce-alpha-enabled-default
* ci-kubernetes-e2e-gci-gce-alpha-features


Once that's updated, we can do `/test pull-kubernetes-e2e-gce-alpha-features` on this PR and see a passing run of the test before merge.
